04)------RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([trace_id@0], 4), input_partitions=1
05)--------AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[trace_id@0 as trace_id], aggr=[max(traces.timestamp)]
06)----------DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]

